Class SyncCirclead

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rogatio.circlead.main.SyncCirclead
  • public class SyncCirclead
extends java.lang.Object
    Start-Class for Synchronizing Systems. Merge of workitems is not ready implemented yet, so FileSynchronizer-Datastorage is deleted on every runtime. Atlassian is main-database and FileSynchronizer is only Json-Workitem-Storage as actual "copy" of Atlassian-Storage
